snippet.title: The Adderall Diaries Official Trailer Reaction Review | James Franco, Amber Heard Movie
snippet.description:
The Adderall Diaries is an upcoming American crime-thriller film written and directed by Pamela Romanowsky, based on a "true-crime memoir" book of the same name by Stephen Elliott. The underlying true crime is the Hans Reiser murder case. The film stars James Franco, Ed Harris and Amber Heard. The film is scheduled to be released on April 15, 2016 in a limited release by A24.
